Requires RabbitMQ. On Ubuntu, install:

1. add X to /etc/apt/sources.list, then
    wget http://www.rabbitmq.com/rabbitmq-signing-key-public.asc
    sudo apt-key add rabbitmq-signing-key-public.asc
    sudo apt-get update
2. sudo apt-get install rabbitmq-server
3. sudo apt-get install python-pip git-core
4. sudo pip install pika==0.9.5

